show.title: Vicious Son in Law, Don't Mess with Me

show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/VZE9D7
show.description: Daughter and husband were indirectly killed by her malicious son-in-law and greedy in-laws, yet even in the aftermath of tragedy, they shamelessly sought to seize her estate, treating her grief as an opportunity for gain. Heartbroken and betrayed, she watched as the people who once called her “mother” and “family” turned into vultures circling her pain.
